full_text:
That close to a commercial transmitter, any device is likely going to 
get a little groundpath interference. For some reason most devices 
are pretty tight against RF interference at higher frequencies, but 
suck at high power long/medium wave signal rejection, especially at 
close range.

thanks
Andy




